Let us get some datasets to use during the development. We will try to create a lib that occludes a dataset with the dataset of another task. In the examples we will use Pets and MNIST.

pets_path = untar_data(URLs.PETS)/"images"
pets_files  = get_image_files(pets_path)

{% endraw %} {% raw %}
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
pets_labeller = using_attr(RegexLabeller(pat = r'^(.*)_\d+.jpg$'), 'name')
vals = list(map(pets_labeller, pets_files))
vocab, o2i = uniqueify(vals, sort=True, bidir=True)
pets = PetTfm(128, vocab, o2i, pets_labeller)
{% endraw %} {% raw %}
